<h2 align="center">OSHIP Setup Steps</h2>

<ol>
<li>Edit the Languages list in src/oship/openehr/utils.py for your applications.</li> 
<li>Place your ADL files in src/oship/openehr/adl <i>(OSHIP comes with the ones for the demo app.)</i></li>
<li>Run the <a href="setup">Setup</a> function to create your python source templates from the ADL files.</li> 
<li>Edit the python source files according to these <a href="editpysrc">instructions</a>.</li> 
<li>Create grok.Viewlets for your new python source files.</li> 
</ol>

